snippet.title: Master System Longplay [232] 20 em 1
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Reinc

20 em 1 (Port.: "20 in 1" ) is a compilation game from Tec Toy that allows players to choose from 20 simplistic games. The title was exclusively released in Brazil as a pack-in game included with later revisions of the Master System. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
